---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HorizontalCard from "../components/HorizontalCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title = "Projects" sideBarActiveItemID="projects">
  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-5">AI & Machine Learning Projects</div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="Vibe Coach - AI Fitness & Rehab Platform"
    img="/vibecoach.png"
    desc="Team Lead, Full-Stack & ML Developer | Oct. 2025"
    url="#"
    badge="NEW"
  />
  <div class="mb-5 ml-2">
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
      <li>Built a full-stack fitness platform with real-time pose analysis using <strong>Google Cloud Video Intelligence API</strong>, <strong>TensorFlow.js PoseNet</strong>, and <strong>OpenAI GPT-4</strong> for personalized coaching feedback</li>
      <li>Designed B2C/B2B systems with integrated dashboards, multi-patient management, and rehab metrics via <strong>Next.js</strong>, <strong>Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth)</strong>, and <strong>Python MediaPipe</strong></li>
      <li>Deployed on <strong>Google Cloud Platform</strong> with static IP and optimized ML pipelines integrating computer vision and natural language models</li>
      <li><strong>Tech Stack:</strong> Next.js, Supabase, Google Cloud Video Intelligence API, TensorFlow.js, OpenAI GPT-4, Python MediaPipe</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  
  <HorizontalCard
    title="Pose Analysis AI Coach"
    img="/post_img.webp"
    desc="Team Lead | Google Developer Build with AI Hackathon - 3rd Place | Apr. 2025"
    url="#"
    badge="3rd Place"
  />
  <div class="mb-5 ml-2">
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
      <li>Built a pose-analysis web app using <strong>Google Cloud Vision API</strong> for keypoint detection and <strong>Gemini Pro</strong> for personalized natural language feedback</li>
      <li>Processed video data and generated prompt chains for enhanced AI coaching feedback</li>
      <li>Deployed with <strong>Streamlit</strong> for real-time user interaction</li>
      <li><strong>Tech Stack:</strong> Google Cloud Vision API, Gemini Pro, Streamlit, Python</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-5 mt-10">Full-Stack Development Projects</div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="XPorter Data Dashboard"
    img="/post_img.webp"
    desc="Software Engineering Intern | Jul. 2025 - Sep. 2025"
    url="#"
  />
  <div class="mb-5 ml-2">
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
      <li>Developed a full-stack data dashboard with <strong>Django</strong> for e-commerce clients to upload and analyze CSVs, automatically cleaning inconsistent data and generating key business metrics</li>
      <li>Built backend pipeline merging data from multiple sources into one unified CSV, reducing manual preprocessing by <strong>80%</strong></li>
      <li>Deployed with <strong>Docker</strong>, <strong>Gunicorn</strong>, and <strong>Nginx</strong> on <strong>AWS EC2</strong> for secure, multi-source production</li>
      <li><strong>Tech Stack:</strong> Django, Docker, Gunicorn, Nginx, AWS EC2, Python, PostgreSQL</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
